Infection Control Nurse / Senior
Infection Control Nurse / Senior
Location:  --Dubai
Salary:  GBP42000 - GBP50000 per annum + Tax Free Infection Control Senior / Nurse, Middle East, Permanent £42-£50,000 Tax Free
Reporting to the Quality Manager, the Infection Control leader will ensure the hospital meets internal and external guidelines. This is an ideal role for an aspiring person to join the team and bring with them western based experience to the hospital. You will have proven experience and capability as an Infection Control Nurse / Supervisor or Manager and be looking to take your skills to the Emirates. An Msc in Infection control or other qualifications are required for this specialist position.
Contact Clive Hutchings at str 0044 2392 322 322 or email your cv to chutchings@strgroup.co.uk
